originalText.text:
I was on therapy with Brook  Hersey over 4 years I had an excellent experience with her approach. She is very professional with a great education and credentials.  She never interferes with client private life , only she does intervention with clients who are neglected by significant others or abused.She is 100% politically correct.  She does provide none judgmental environment without pretending.
She is a wonderful psychologist who never concentrates only about $.
I had even sliding scale when insurance benefits did not cover me fully.
Best work she done with me .
